*******How to run*********
Note--> The zip file containing the required directories have already been downloaded into the Run_this directory. There's no need to add anything into that.
1.Open the Run_this directory
2.Run "script_main"
-->bash script_main
This will run the other scripts in the required order, and will solve both the problems, from scratch

The individual scripts and the steps detailing the script contents are also present in the respective question folder.
